snippet.title: “New VIRTUA FIGHTER Project” pre-development concept video
snippet.description:
We're excited to unveil a special preview of the concept video for the "New VIRTUA FIGHTER Project." This video was presented at the Consumer Electronics Show, the world's largest electronics trade fair, during the keynote speech by NVIDIA's founder and CEO, Jensen Huang.
* Please note that this is a concept video created before development began. The actual gameplay and characters may differ from what is shown. 
 
Follow the official Virtua Fighter X account
https://x.com/VF_SEGA 
 
Official Virtua Fighter Website
https://virtua-fighter.com/revo/en/ 
 
NVIDIA Website
https://www.nvidia.com/ 
 
Join the official Virtua Fighter Discord Server 
https://discord.gg/GvPrfJXHVg 
Connect with fellow players and stay updated on all things Virtua Fighter here!! 
 
#virtuafighter #vf5revo #steam #legacyvf #fightinggames #sega
